waydroid-helper (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New controller subsystem for gaming controls
  * Modern event-driven architecture for input handling
  * Support for key/mouse mapping to Android controls
  * Gaming control widgets (aim, fire, directional pad, macros)
  * Wayland platform integration improvements
  * Enhanced extension management system
  * Bug fixes and stability improvements

